# Simple if
# Question:
# Determine the day of the week based on a given number (1 for Monday, 2 for Tuesday, etc.).
# Print the corresponding day of the week or "Invalid day" if the input is not in the range [1, 7].

# Answer:
day_number = int(input("Enter a number (1-7): "))

if 1 <= day_number <= 7:
    days_of_week = ["Monday", "Tuesday", "Wednesday", "Thursday", "Friday", "Saturday", "Sunday"]
    print("Day of the week:", days_of_week[day_number - 1])
else:
    print("Invalid day")
